snippet.title: Norn9: Var Commons - Official Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Fan favorite Norn9: Var Commons is coming to Nintendo Switch, followed by fandisc Last Era, localized for the first time in the West! In Var Commons, child prodigy Sorata finds himself swept back in time to a mysterious ship with three young women and eight other men on an adventure to uncover the secrets that lie in Norn! Last Era continues the team’s adventures in three exciting parts. 

Revealed at AX 2022
More info to Come
